Subject“M/T Heather Knutsen” and “M/T Jasmine Knutsen” Repair or Alteration Remission Order
Precis"M/T HEATHER KNUTSEN" AND "M/T JASMINE KNUTSEN" JASMINE KNUTSEN REPAIR OR ALTERATION REMISSION ORDER, 2018, in order to remit customs duties paid by Canship for maintenance and repair work performed offshore since the work could not be undertaken in Canada due to a lack of facilities large enough to accommodate the two tankers.
